    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Made from the ground bones of ghouls or other cannibalistic creatures processed into a green-gray paste, gnawbone toxin imparts an insatiable desire to consume the flesh of intelligent creatures. If the victim eats at least a mouthful of humanoid flesh, it ignores the enfeebled condition from gnawbone toxin for 1 minute. Victims under the effect of gnawbone toxin regain only half as many Hit Points from healing effects unless they\u2019ve eaten at least a mouthful of humanoid flesh in the last minute.",
        "level": 11,
